Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.17,0:00:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's... dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.72,0:00:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The devil...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.93,0:00:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The devil has come to this town!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.15,0:00:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. I'll go in first.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.86,0:00:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You cover me from the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.91,0:00:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Our top priority is to save Inspector Lunge.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.16,0:00:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.79,0:00:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.25,0:00:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wim.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.54,0:00:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.00,0:00:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,A woman came to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.59,0:00:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.13,0:00:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,She went to the vampire's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.09,0:01:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,A woman who looked just like one\Nof the twins in the pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.72,0:01:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the twins in the pictures? Nina?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.02,0:01:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Her name is Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.77,0:01:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So now her name is Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.44,0:01:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl is now known as Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.11,0:01:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Nina Fortner.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.33,0:01:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What a nice name.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.21,0:01:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You always told me to cherish my name, Mr. Poppe.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.10,0:01:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you see my dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.64,0:01:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't find him anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.02,0:01:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. We're doing something important right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.11,0:01:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,but once it's over, we'll look for him right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.28,0:01:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,My dad hasn't killed anyone, has he?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.99,0:02:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he hasn't, Wim.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.57,0:02:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Your dad isn't someone who would do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.37,0:02:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.37,0:02:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Hide in that store over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.48,0:02:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Take Wim and find cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.28,0:02:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We finally meet again, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.38,0:03:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us die.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.23,0:03:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us die...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.15,0:03:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.63,0:05:29.68,Monster-Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(750,500)\pos(360,340)}Scenery for a Doomsday
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.92,0:05:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.88,0:05:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to find him. Franz Bonaparta.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.80,0:05:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then, at the Red Rose Mansion, he...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.02,0:05:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.48,0:05:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is going to forget what they just saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.78,0:06:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Run far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.95,0:06:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,As far as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.29,0:06:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,People can become anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.39,0:06:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You two are beautiful treasures.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.18,0:06:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you mustn't become monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.86,0:06:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what he said to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.53,0:06:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I... That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.00,0:06:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Poppe!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.84,0:06:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Poppe!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.88,0:06:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Poppe!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.43,0:07:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Franz Bonaparta.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.86,0:07:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Roberto!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.37,0:07:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Run, Wim!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.73,0:07:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Show me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.36,0:07:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,the scenery of doomsday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.70,0:08:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.95,0:08:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,will never see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.84,0:08:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Wim!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.59,0:08:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Get away from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.98,0:08:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.27,0:08:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,According to you, lives are equal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.36,0:08:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I live today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.28,0:08:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But, you must have realized it by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.99,0:08:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing people are equal in...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.16,0:08:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,is death.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.47,0:09:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.18,0:09:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The scenery of doomsday.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.77,0:10:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.15,0:10:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma, you mustn't shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.66,0:10:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.38,0:10:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.00,0:10:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.88,0:10:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we were the only people on Earth, I'd forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.81,0:10:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That is my message to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.81,0:10:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.23,0:10:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something you can never get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.11,0:10:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.99,0:10:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma's going to shoot me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.99,0:10:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.47,0:11:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.31,0:11:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.35,0:11:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.69,0:11:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.28,0:12:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The devil...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.07,0:12:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The devil has come to this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.07,0:12:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He has come to kill everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.26,0:12:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Wim...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.43,0:12:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.06,0:12:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,My son.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.60,0:12:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.07,0:12:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.45,0:13:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.42,0:13:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.21,0:13:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Let him go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.01,0:13:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Get away from my son!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.02,0:13:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the D-KMIF. We've landed\Non the west side of Ruhenheim.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.53,0:13:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We've confirmed that the east side is safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.04,0:13:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Secure any citizens that you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.21,0:13:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.29,0:13:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there any survivors?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.21,0:14:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Our DNN news crew has finally made it\Nto town, located in the hills of the south.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.05,0:14:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a shocking incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.30,0:14:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This town has been wiped out in some sort of slaughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.68,0:14:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened in this quiet town in South Germany?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.23,0:14:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. We currently have only one\Nperson to press charges against.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.03,0:14:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Herbert Knaup, age 38, unemployed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.07,0:14:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.45,0:14:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He has confessed to a crime. He shot a young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.25,0:14:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad only shot him to save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.33,0:14:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that he's pretty drunk
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.92,0:14:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and he committed the crime because a monster\Nwith horns and seven heads attacked his son.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.85,0:14:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been saying nothing but nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.06,0:14:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.31,0:14:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Please respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.19,0:14:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, it went out again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.65,0:15:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.28,0:15:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just... I don't understand what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.66,0:15:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,A young man named Johan destroyed\Nthis town in order to commit suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.71,0:15:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Gillen, can you explain it so that we can understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.55,0:15:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It will take a long time to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.42,0:15:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And even after that, you might still not understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.81,0:15:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We've secured an injured police\Nofficer in the Versteck Hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.40,0:15:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,How is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.44,0:15:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir! I don't think his life is in danger,\Nbut his sense is messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.74,0:15:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit. There's not a single officer who\Ncan explain what happened here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.54,0:15:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There is one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.83,0:15:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I know everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.50,0:15:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.04,0:16:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Inspector Lunge from the BKA.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.13,0:16:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have my badge with me, but check with the BKA.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.72,0:16:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Roberto.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.81,0:16:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.39,0:16:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the real culprit here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.98,0:16:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to deliver the final blow, but he lost consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.65,0:16:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I got away from him and headed downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.41,0:16:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard his voice from behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.03,0:16:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,In the next instant, he hit me in the back of the\Nhead with his pistol and knocked me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.00,0:16:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He then said this,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.09,0:16:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,"I still can't see it."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.84,0:16:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,"The World of the End."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.88,0:16:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll talk later after you get treated.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.81,0:16:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't cry. We're safe now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.60,0:17:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me. I need to confirm your identities.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.11,0:17:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We're the Hennigs from Erft Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.57,0:17:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my wife Franka.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.99,0:17:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any identification?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.82,0:17:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.37,0:17:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.54,0:17:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.79,0:17:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.67,0:17:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The lotto ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.29,0:17:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.55,0:17:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I put it in my pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.51,0:17:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go look for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.01,0:17:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.51,0:17:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I dropped it somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.05,0:17:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.56,0:17:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.19,0:17:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Just living here together...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.48,0:17:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,is enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.70,0:18:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... That proof of identification...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.29,0:18:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll ask for it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.43,0:18:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, any more survivors?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.60,0:18:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,There are some.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.77,0:18:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.19,0:18:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to confirm your identities.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.45,0:18:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to every house.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.16,0:18:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,There might still be survivors.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.49,0:18:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.70,0:18:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.21,0:18:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.17,0:18:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.64,0:19:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.73,0:19:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.27,0:19:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No, with that head wound, he'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.69,0:19:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We couldn't save him even if we had\Na brilliant brain surgeon here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.78,0:19:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No. There is one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.12,0:19:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Call him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.00,0:19:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We have some questions to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.75,0:19:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.97,0:19:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt. He's the wanted criminal...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.64,0:19:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.52,0:19:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Dr. Tenma, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.48,0:19:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.48,0:19:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.32,0:19:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector Lunge from the BKA asked for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.57,0:20:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He wanted me to tell you that there's\Nan important patient waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.67,0:20:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,My dad is not a murderer.
